      <purpose>To record a suggestion, advice or proposal about the most suitable treatment for each patient with age-related macular degeneration.</purpose>
      <keywords>advice</keywords>
      <keywords>proposal</keywords>
      <keywords>suggestion</keywords>
      <keywords>treatment</keywords>
      <keywords>age-related macular degeneration</keywords>
      <use>Use to record a suggestion, advice or proposal about the treatment of age-related macular degeneration, at a specific point in time of its clinical history.

The statement is considered only at the time it is registered. That is to say, the treatment can change over time depending on the progression of the disease.</use>
      <misuse />
      <copyright>© openEHR Foundation</copyright>
